@node "openconsoledevice" "Utils/ConsoleUtils/OpenConsleDevice"

    Utils/ConsoleUtils/OpenConsoleDevice

    NAME
        OpenConsoleDevice - assign a valid value to ConsoleBase

    SYNOPSIS
        PROCEDURE OpenConsoleDevice;

    DESCRIPTION
        This routine just opens the console.device without attaching
        it to a window, so you can make calls to RawKeyConvert and
        CDInputHandler.  It also needs to be open for DeadKeyConvert.

    EXAMPLE
        see @{" Examples/SmallCom.p " alink "PCQ:Examples/SmallCom.p/main" 0}
            @{" Examples/Map.p      " alink "PCQ:Examples/Map.p/main" 0}
            @{" Examples/3d.p       " alink "PCQ:Examples/3d.p/main" 0}

    INPUTS
        None

    RESULTS
        None

    SEE ALSO
        @{" CloseConsoleDevice " link "closeconsoledevice" 0} @{" DeadKeyConvert     " link "PCQ:Hyper/utils/deadkeyconvert.guide/deadkeyconvert" 0}

